TripAdvisor sees ability to make hotel
reservations directly from mobile app in 2014, “unclear” if
co. will make acquisitions in space, CFO Julie Bradley says in
interview.
•TRIP won’t be OTA, though user interface will be direct;
booking partners will fulfill reservation, “but from a consumer
standpoint they’ll be able to one-click and with their credit
card information on file”
•40% of TRIP traffic is on mobile or smartphone, has >100m
“monthly uniques"; introduced iPhone, Android app Oct. 3
•Sees growth in LatAm, Asia Pacific, where customers tend to
research online.  NI VISIBLE 